Program: Outlook
Title: Cholesterol Free People in Italy
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbr00
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Italians from Limone sul Garda with a cholesterol scavenger gene that can help to develop an anti-cholesterol drug . Also in the programme, the Indian origins of the Romani language and turning out the lights in Colombia in protest against rebel forces fighting the government.